    "name": "Mesh Independence Study for CFD Hemolysis Model",
    "description": "Systematic mesh refinement study conducted across three mesh densities (coarse 2.1M cells, medium 5.8M cells, fine 14.2M cells) to establish discretization error bounds for the centrifugal pump CFD model. Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for shear stress and velocity magnitude at five operating points spanning the CPB flow-speed envelope. Study performed using ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 with k-omega SST turbulence closure.",
    "activityType": "MeshRefinementStudy",
    "startedAtTime": "2025-09-10T08:00:00Z",
